      "writtenOn": "2020-07-09T22:51:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this strategy might work for a single person team (as long as the person does not forget what they wrote yesterday)\n\nbut it does not work well for a team of multiple people - others might not know that this code was written in a non-generic place, so they might write it again. In the worst case, they would do the same, so identical code is written in a non-generic place for the second time and the code is still not reused.\n\nit is also easier to read and review more modular code",
